      "title": "[负面] i picked up this game hoping for like lovecraftian...",
      "summary": "i picked up this game hoping for like lovecraftian horror in a card game style. what i got was a complete ripoff of reverse 1999  (and to a lesser extent honkai star rail) with ai generated text. i can point out so many characters that have the same design elements or concepts as either r99 or hoyoverse characters. it's unintuitive, the story is hard to follow (and i say this as someone who loved r99 and other games with convoluted or hard-to-unravel stories)...etc. just go play reverse 1999 instead, it has more interesting antagonists as well",
